    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"let it consume you\"... i don't think i can do that. i'm just so tired of fighting it. it feels like there's no actual way to \"be still\" without the pain being right there. i just want it to be over. i just want to finally be at peace and stop feeling like this.",
